    Program ........ Cacti User Group Plugin
    Version ........ 0.3
    Purpose ........ Extends Cacti to Support Multiple User Groups

*******************************************************************************/


----[ Purpose

    There is currently no support for User Groups in Cacti.  This plugin
    corrects that.

----[ Features

    Allow administrators to create Multiple User Groups.

----[ Prerequisites

    Cacti PIA 2.8++
	Patches not necessary for Cacti v0.8.8 or above

----[ Installation

    http://docs.cacti.net/plugins.install

----[ Additional Help?

    If you need additional help, please go to http://forums.cacti.net

----[ Possible Bugs?

    If you figure out this problem, let me know!!!

----[ Future Changes

    Got any ideas or complaints, see the forums

